<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>About</title>
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.1.1/css/all.min.css"
    />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />

    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        font-family: "Montserrat", sans-serif;
      }

      #head {
        background: linear-gradient(
          to right,
          rgb(249, 18, 226),
          rgb(12, 194, 226),
          rgb(249, 18, 226)
        );
        color: white;
        padding: 10px;
        justify-content: center;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 1.3rem;
      }
      .para1 {
        padding: 10px;
        font-size: 20px;
        display: flex;
        margin-top: 20px;
        border-bottom: solid rgb(249, 18, 226) 2px;
        text-align: justify;
        justify-content: space-evenly;
      }
      .para1 img,
      .para1 p,
      .para2 img,
      .para2 p {
        padding: 1rem;
      }
      .image {
        width: 26%;
      }
      .para2 {
        padding: 10px;
        font-size: 20px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: row-reverse;
        margin-top: 20px;
        border-bottom: solid rgb(12, 194, 226) 2px;
        text-align: justify;
        justify-content: space-evenly;
      }
      .para1 img,
      .para2 img {
        border-radius: 2rem;
      }
      .foot {
        background: linear-gradient(
          to right,
          rgb(249, 18, 226),
          rgb(12, 194, 226),
          rgb(249, 18, 226)
        );
        align-items: center;
      }
      .foot i {
        color: white;
        padding: 0.6rem;
        gap: 30px;
      }
      #copy {
        float: right;
        color: white;
        font-size: 24px;
        padding: 0.6rem;
      }
      .text {
        width: 65%;
      }
      .text .first {
        color: rgb(249, 18, 226);
      }
      .text .second {
        color: rgb(12, 194, 226);
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div id="head"><h1>ABOUT</h1></div>
    <div class="para1">
      <div class="text">
        <h2 class="first">How customer can be benefited?</h2>
        <p>
          This website allows users to book rooms in many hotels across India
          from anywhere. Customers can register themselves on our website and
          then they will become eligible to access all other features of the
          website.Travellers can book rooms on a computer by using online
          security to protect their privacy and financial information and by
          using several online travel agents to compare prices and facilities a
          different hotels.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="image">
        <img
          src="https://blog.ipleaders.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/hotel-booking-mobile-app-development-1140x648.jpg"
          alt="img"
          width="100%"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="para2">
      <div class="text">
        <h2 class="second">How hotels can be benefited?</h2>
        <p>
          This website allows hotels to sell their serives to more persons
          across India and earn profit. Every hotel's goal is to sell more rooms
          and make a profit. Yet, without an online booking system, you will
          have to rely on phone calls and walk-ins only to make reservations. An
          online booking platform is a necessity. That's why we would like to
          point out the key benefits every good hotel booking system should
          bring you.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="image">
        <img
          src="https://images.yourstory.com/production/document_image/mystoryimage/3ks4f7ym-Book-Online-Hotels-at-affordable-price.jpg"
          alt="img"
          width="100%"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="para1">
      <div class="text">
        <h2 class="first">Hotels at cheapest price!</h2>
        <p>
          Customers can books hotels at cheapest rate as possible. Available
          Rate (BAR), also known as Best Rate Guaranteed (BRG), is a pricing
          mechanism used by hotels and hotel chains. It was introduced as a
          result of the hotel industry mimicking the airline industry, which
          sets price by forecasting demand.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="image">
        <img src="cheap(1).jpeg" alt="img" width="100%" height="220rem" />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="para2">
      <div class="text">
        <h2 class="second">Compare hotels and choose best deals</h2>
        <p>
          This feature allows customers to compare different hotels and choose
          best deals from available ones. They can compare features, facilities
          and prices of different hotels. Finding best hotel is an important and
          difficult task for any trip. Our website helps you to find best deals
          at cheapest rate which sets price by forecasting demand.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="image">
        <img
          src="https://hardbacon.ca/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/hotel-pmo0tnalnk02ob1sckrzbmy0zrqehpp6ue5z322wd0.png"
          alt="img"
          width="100%"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
